{"declarations":[{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/DocString/Builtin/Postponed.html#Lean.Doc.DeferredCheck.run\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Doc</span>.<span class=\"name\">DeferredCheck</span>.<span class=\"name\">run</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">inPackage</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.Name\">Name</a> → <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">shouldCheck</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/DocString/DeferredCheck.html#Lean.Doc.DeferredCheck\">DeferredCheck</a> → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/CoreM.html#Lean.Core.CoreM\">CoreM</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></span></span> := <span class=\"fn\">fun (<span class=\"fn\">x</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/DocString/DeferredCheck.html#Lean.Doc.DeferredCheck\">DeferredCheck</a>) =&gt; <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Pure.pure\">pure</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool.true\">true</a></span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/CoreM.html#Lean.Core.CoreM\">CoreM</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Array\">Array</a> (<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.Name\">Name</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Prod\">×</a> <a href=\"./Lean/DocString/DeferredCheck.html#Lean.Doc.DeferredCheck\">DeferredCheck</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Prod\">×</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Message.html#Lean.MessageData\">MessageData</a>))</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Runs the deferred docstring checks owned by modules satisfying `inPackage`.\n\nReturns the checks that failed together with the module they belong to and the error that each\nproduced. `#[]` indicates success.\n\nOnly checks that satisfy `shouldCheck` are run.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/DocString/Builtin/Postponed.html#Lean.Doc.DeferredCheck.run","kind":"def","line":146,"name":"Lean.Doc.DeferredCheck.run","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Elab/DocString/Builtin/Postponed.lean#L146-L184"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/DocString/Builtin/Postponed.html#Lean.Doc.DeferredCheck.addBuiltinHandler\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Doc</span>.<span class=\"name\">DeferredCheck</span>.<span class=\"name\">addBuiltinHandler</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">key</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.Name\">Name</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">impl</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Elab/DocString/Builtin/Postponed.html#Lean.Doc.DeferredCheckHandler\">DeferredCheckHandler</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/System/IO.html#IO\">IO</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Unit\">Unit</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Adds a builtin deferred check handler.\n\nShould be run during initialization.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/DocString/Builtin/Postponed.html#Lean.Doc.DeferredCheck.addBuiltinHandler","kind":"def","line":78,"name":"Lean.Doc.DeferredCheck.addBuiltinHandler","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Elab/DocString/Builtin/Postponed.lean#L78-L84"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">opaque</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/DocString/Builtin/Postponed.html#Lean.Doc.DeferredCheck.builtinHandlers\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Doc</span>.<span class=\"name\">DeferredCheck</span>.<span class=\"name\">builtinHandlers</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/System/IO.html#IO.Ref\">IO.Ref</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Lean/Data/NameMap/Basic.html#Lean.NameMap\">NameMap</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Elab/DocString/Builtin/Postponed.html#Lean.Doc.DeferredCheckHandler\">DeferredCheckHandler</a>)</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Builtin deferred check handlers, for bootstrapping. Maps a check's data type name to its handler,\nwhich is available before the defining module is imported.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/DocString/Builtin/Postponed.html#Lean.Doc.DeferredCheck.builtinHandlers","kind":"opaque","line":72,"name":"Lean.Doc.DeferredCheck.builtinHandlers","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Elab/DocString/Builtin/Postponed.lean#L72-L76"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">opaque</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/DocString/Builtin/Postponed.html#Lean.Doc.DeferredCheck.handlerExt\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Doc</span>.<span class=\"name\">DeferredCheck</span>.<span class=\"name\">handlerExt</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/EnvExtension.html#Lean.SimplePersistentEnvExtension\">SimplePersistentEnvExtension</a> (<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.Name\">Name</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Prod\">×</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.Name\">Name</a>) <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Lean/Data/NameMap/Basic.html#Lean.NameMap\">NameMap</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.Name\">Name</a>)</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Maps the name of a deferred check's data (the value of `Dynamic.typeName`) to the declaration of its\n`DeferredCheckHandler`. The data type is the dispatch key, so at most on